1
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,039
Young Madam.

2
00:01:28,039 --> 00:01:29,640
The Lu family has a business banquet tonight.

3
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,720
The Young Master left instructions before he went out

4
00:01:30,720 --> 00:01:32,050
for you to prepare well.

5
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:34,759
Rich families always put on such a show.

6
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:36,039
I'm just a boxer.

7
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:38,160
When have I ever seen this kind of business banquet?

8
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:38,920
Young Madam.

9
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,450
Let me help you get dressed.

10
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:41,680
Since you married into the family,

11
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:44,120
I've always been the one to help you dress and do your makeup.

12
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:46,759
She used to serve the original owner.

13
00:01:46,759 --> 00:01:49,360
I should try to get some information out of her.

14
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:53,170
I'll put it on later.

15
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,530
Come, let's talk first.

16
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,840
Let's talk.

17
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,479
Change it later.

18
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,120
No rush. Have a seat.

19
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,840
I can't sit.

20
00:01:58,840 --> 00:01:59,960
Sit down.

21
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:04,040
Your name is...

22
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,440
Tang Lili?

23
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,920
Lili, right?

24
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,280
You usually take care of me.

25
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,120
Yes.

26
00:02:10,600 --> 00:02:11,520
After I married into this family,

27
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,800
how have I been getting along with the Lus?

28
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,960
Young Madam, why are you asking me?

29
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:20,280
I just feel that after I married into this family,

30
00:02:20,280 --> 00:02:22,360
I don't fit in with them.

31
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,440
I'm just asking you for some gossip

32
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:26,120
so I can blend in better.

33
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,920
Your marriage with the Young Master

34
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,600
was arranged by Master Shen and Master Lu

35
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,280
for a business partnership.

36
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:36,520
The Young Master was against it from the start.

37
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,120
And there's Cousin Su Yuran.

38
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:40,260
She's always wanted to marry him.

39
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,120
So after you married him...

40
00:02:43,480 --> 00:02:45,920
Anyway, you must always be careful of her.

41
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,680
If worse comes to worst,

42
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:48,840
just avoid her.

43
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,600
You've endured it all this time,

44
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,640
so just bear with it today.

45
00:02:53,640 --> 00:02:54,400
Today?

46
00:02:55,079 --> 00:02:56,000
She said

47
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,200
she arranged a special segment for you,

48
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,770
wanting you to perform a dance at the banquet.

49
00:03:00,880 --> 00:03:02,210
[Presenting the dance]

50
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,560
Be careful.

51
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,320
No.

52
00:03:11,880 --> 00:03:13,320
Why is your dress torn?

53
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:16,320
It's strangling me.

54
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,480
Of course it's torn.

55
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,920
Who picked the size?

56
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,280
Your cousin sent it.

57
00:03:21,720 --> 00:03:24,040
She said she designed it for you herself.

58
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,040
It suits you best.

59
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,840
Her name is...

60
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,360
Su...

61
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,160
Su... Su Yuran.

62
00:03:32,880 --> 00:03:35,240
The one you just told me about,

63
00:03:35,240 --> 00:03:37,600
Su Yuran, right?

64
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,600
I'll choose you today.

65
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:41,320
Su

66
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,160
Yu

67
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:43,040
ran.

68
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,680
Cousin.

69
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,120
The contract for the luxury brand agency rights,

70
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,960
wasn't it supposed to be transferred to me today?

71
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,560
Why is it stuck in the legal department?

72
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,400
The legal department said they need Lu Jingheng's signature.

73
00:04:00,400 --> 00:04:02,240
I told them it was Dad's verbal authorization,

74
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:02,760
but they wouldn't accept it.

75
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,840
What can I do?

76
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,300
Who do they think they are?

77
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,700
This is the Lu family's business,

78
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,880
and you're the second young master of the Lu family.

79
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,540
It's not their place to speak.

80
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:14,720
You have a harsh tongue, Cousin.

81
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:16,680
We worked together, so let's part on good terms.

82
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:19,480
Are you worried I won't find anything against the legal department

83
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,920
to make them pack up and leave tomorrow?

84
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,380
Everything goes as usual.

85
00:04:22,880 --> 00:04:24,360
Then thank you, Cousin.

86
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,480
To our future cooperation, cheers.

87
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,040
Brother Jingheng.

88
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,840
Brother.

89
00:04:42,440 --> 00:04:43,770
Verbal authorization?

90
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,840
Without written authorization,

91
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:47,400
what does the Lu family's business

92
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,680
have to do with you?

93
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:49,640
Brother, what you said

94
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:50,840
is too bossy.

95
00:04:51,640 --> 00:04:53,120
Dad clearly said before he went abroad...

96
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,560
I know exactly

97
00:04:54,960 --> 00:04:56,220
what you are planning.

98
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:58,200
As long as I'm in the Lu Group,

99
00:04:58,840 --> 00:05:00,240
you have no say.

100
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,160
Brother.

101
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:04,160
We are family, must it be like this?

102
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,080
Family?

103
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:08,040
The profit-sharing ratio you gave to the Su Group

104
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,840
is at least 3% higher than the external rate.

105
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,500
Taking the Lu Group's profits

106
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:13,000
to do others a favor?

107
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,560
The contract is void.

108
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,440
Otherwise,

109
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:20,240
I will ask the legal department to issue a letter of accountability right now.

110
00:05:20,240 --> 00:05:21,040
You choose.

111
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:23,480
Jingheng, don't be angry.

112
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,360
Our two families cooperating

113
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,640
isn't a bad thing.

114
00:05:26,640 --> 00:05:28,680
I will personally take charge of the women's clothing design.

115
00:05:28,680 --> 00:05:30,280
Why did she come dressed like this?

116
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:31,800
Yeah, why did she dress like this?

117
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,800
So embarrassing.

118
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,680
Why did she dress like this

119
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:37,280
to attend the banquet?

120
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,680
So embarrassing.

121
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,060
How could you come dressed like this?

122
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,520
This is the Lu family's banquet.

123
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,240
Wearing sportswear here,

124
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:57,440
aren't you embarrassing our Lu family?

125
00:05:58,320 --> 00:05:59,120
Jingheng.

126
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,000
I specially designed

127
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,680
a set of haute couture women's clothing for her.

128
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:05,200
I didn't expect my sister-in-law to be so clueless.

129
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:07,080
You designed that trashy dress?

130
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,120
I was just wondering

131
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,120
how a size small could strangle a cow.

132
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,680
It's because

133
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:12,720
of self-righteous designers like you.

134
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,680
No wonder.

135
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:16,320
Who can wear a size small in women's clothing nowadays?

136
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,920
And you call it haute couture?

137
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:19,480
You really know how to flatter yourself.

138
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,320
Cousin.

139
00:06:20,640 --> 00:06:22,120
I was only doing it for her own good.

140
00:06:22,120 --> 00:06:23,680
How can she be so ungrateful

141
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,040
and even play the victim?

142
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:26,970
Sister-in-law,

143
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:29,120
Yuran means well.

144
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,920
As for you,

145
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,940
why are you so angry today?

146
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,360
Please excuse us.

147
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:45,720
We're just having a family chat.

148
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,440
Today,

149
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,520
my sister-in-law, Shen Zhixia,

150
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:53,120
is going to perform a song for everyone.

151
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:56,320
Show everyone your talent.

152
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,370
Sister-in-law,

153
00:07:03,520 --> 00:07:05,920
I specially hired a musician for you.

154
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,440
Please don't let us all down.

155
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,480
Su Yuran,

156
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,480
how dare you mess with her.

157
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,920
Yuran, look, my brother misunderstood again.

158
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:16,450
We're just trying to liven up the atmosphere.

159
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:17,840
If you're worried, Brother,

160
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,920
why don't you join my sister-in-law?

161
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,880
I don't need him.

162
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,920
I want to try it with you.

163
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,120
Sure.

164
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:36,170
To dance with my sister-in-law

165
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,320
is an honor.

166
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,320
Cousin.

167
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:47,680
Shen Zhixia.

168
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:49,120
Who do you think you are?

169
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,120
You are nothing but

170
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:52,320
a dog raised by the Lu family.

171
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:01,640
Yeah, so dramatic.

172
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,920
How embarrassing.

173
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,560
Shen Zhixia.

174
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:13,840
I'm so bored.

175
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:16,450
I'm hungry, I'm going to get something to eat.

176
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,040
Mr. Lu,

177
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,440
Young Madam is indeed

178
00:08:20,440 --> 00:08:22,080
a bit different today.

179
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:25,800
She used to only pretend to be obedient in front of me.

180
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,330
I didn't expect that today,

181
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:29,980
she would actually protect herself.

182
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:31,720
Interesting.

183
00:08:32,720 --> 00:08:33,880
I'm starving.

184
00:08:33,880 --> 00:08:35,520
So much good food.

185
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:38,240
It wasn't a wasted trip.

186
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,080
You...

187
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,240
Why do you walk without making a sound,

188
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,880
like a ghost?

189
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:51,520
You are different from usual today.

190
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:54,300
Why did your skills suddenly become so good?

191
00:08:55,680 --> 00:08:57,600
I was scrolling through short videos a couple of days ago

192
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,800
and learned a few moves.

193
00:08:58,800 --> 00:08:59,640
I'm gifted.

194
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,480
Short videos?

195
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,600
Could they teach you to throw someone to the ground so neatly,

196
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:09,800
giving Lu Jingxi no chance to struggle?

197
00:09:13,240 --> 00:09:14,560
Like I said, I'm gifted.

198
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:15,360
Besides,

199
00:09:15,680 --> 00:09:17,840
Lu Jingxi may look strong,

200
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,560
but he's actually very weak.

201
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,320
He's very weak?

202
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:23,000
How do you know?

203
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,440
Kicking him really hurt.

204
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,440
I pulled a muscle,

205
00:09:29,560 --> 00:09:30,760
and my back hurts too.

206
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:34,040
It hurts.

207
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,240
It hurts.

208
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,320
Stop pretending.

209
00:09:36,440 --> 00:09:37,570
Go home and recover.

210
00:09:37,760 --> 00:09:39,160
It hurts, bro.

211
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,120
It really hurts, bro.

212
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:52,160
Lu Jingheng.

213
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:53,800
What are you doing? Put me down.

214
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,560
Put me down.

215
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:56,680
Young Master.

216
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:59,080
Quick, quick, quick. Put me down.

217
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,880
I'm fine now.

218
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,090
Are you really fine?

219
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,160
Completely fine.

220
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,120
Young Master, Young Madam.

221
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:11,800
Bad news. Master has returned.

222
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:13,480
He heard about the banquet tonight

223
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,840
and is angry now.

224
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,280
I got it.

